        <button onclick="document.getElementById('refund-overlay').remove()" style="padding:11px;background:#f1f5f9;border:none;border-radius:11px;color:#475569;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;">لا، لم يُسترد</button>
